## Planet Zenile

<sub>Help me come up with a better name.</sub> This is my first map published on SC2mapster. This is not finished and will be updated a lot. I need some help with some stuff in the editor.

### Summary

You have recently arrived on this planet. Time to start your adventure...

### Places I need help in

#### Achievements

Which is better:

- Achievements through triggers 
- Achievements through data and triggers I need help with making a dialog to show which achievements you have unlocked. I can probably do the bank by myself.
